OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A woman from north Wales with anorexia 
OL,6, has said she believes she will die     
OL,7, without specialist treatment which is  
OL,8, only available privately in England.   
OL,10,FAmy Ellis from Broughton, Flintshire,  
OL,11,Fis trying to raise thousands of pounds 
OL,12,Fto fund the treatment after being told 
OL,13,Fit would not be paid for by the NHS.   
OL,15,FShe is now cared for by her mum and    
OL,16,Fneeds mobility aids to get around.     
OL,18,FThe Welsh government said every health 
OL,19,Fboard had received funding to improve  
OL,20,Feating disorder services.              
